{"tid":1232904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戰 略 性 撤 退! 入黑後對我邊嚴重不利","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T17:07:16.000Z","uid":106043,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"994475cabd9e0f95f69a1a817e008f14c0626ef7","tid":1232904,"uid":106043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入黑後少記者<br />\n<br />\n影嘢都影唔清死無對證</span></span></strong><br />\n我木依家贏緊輿論戰係靠記者有證據先至支撐到我哋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人數大量減少，畀人捉都難救<br />\n<br />\n朝早大家消耗咁多體力，依家返警犬啱啱開波<br />\n<br />\n仲有可能會有鬼，出面個post講話有中年大陸人著黑衫入境<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入黑對我哋極度不利<br />\n撤退留力</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"502f9057d3643177fa023b1f0728505851724174","tid":1232904,"uid":53870,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"我地既目標係立法會<br />\n唔係海富唔係政總<br />\n今日一定要和平遊行<br />\n唔好再好似69夜晚咁<br />\n唔該大家唔可以係又衝唔係又衝<br />\n會比位人地入 我地手足一個都不能少呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1982c8f3d2cc55976644029d4092a48d20c19c","tid":1232904,"uid":106043,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"咪撚送頭呀<br />\n之前6月9號出完黎，之後都係6月12號先出嚟勇武<br />\n<br />\n佢哋依家又搵鬼放火 又有大量黑警喺度聚集緊。擺明係個局，你入去就送頭。<br />\n<br />\n sorry太心急打錯好多字"},{"pid":"6a23252ae015eded43badb0b641a4fac7c01bd73","tid":1232904,"uid":106043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"留力<br />\n天光先行動"},{"pid":"9e43802de487a48c83ca2e8aabb6b55a84f5fea7","tid":1232904,"uid":41477,"li